notes:
Works great out of the box, but it's highly recommended to turn on the multithreaded rendeing option in in-game options (otherwise, FPS slowdown is possible).

3D battles also work (with minor glitch after loading).

Also I have the following libs installed: https://www.gloriouseggroll.tv/how-to-get-out-of-wine-dependency-hell/. But it should work without them, at least it worked perfectly on vanilla wine previously.
